    <div class="help-section">
        <h3>Account Management</h3>
        <p>Having trouble managing your account? You can <strong>update your profile</strong>, change your password, or view your order history through your profile page. If you've forgotten your password, simply click on the "Forgot Password" link during login.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-section">
        <h3>Order Issues</h3>
        <p>If you're facing issues with an order, such as tracking or delivery problems, check your order status by logging into your account. If your order has not been delivered on time, please contact our support team via the Contact Us page.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-section">
        <h3>Payment Issues</h3>
        <p>We accept multiple payment methods such as credit cards, PayPal, and bank transfers. If you're facing payment issues, double-check your payment method and try again. If the issue persists, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
    </div>

