        <h3>Shipping & Delivery</h3>
        <p>We offer worldwide shipping! For standard orders, expect delivery within 5-7 business days. You will receive a tracking number via email once your order has been shipped. For expedited shipping, please refer to the shipping details on the checkout page.</p>
